---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact APIRank | AI API Questions, Partnerships, Corrections"
  description="Contact APIRank for partnership inquiries, pricing corrections, content suggestions, or technical questions about AI API providers."
  canonicalUrl="https://apirank.vip/contact/"
>
  <div class="bg-gray-50 border-b border-gray-200">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-4">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-blue-600">Home</a>
        <span>›</span>
        <span class="text-gray-900 font-medium">Contact</span>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Contact APIRank</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
        We're a small team (mostly me, Jason) and we read every message. Response time is usually 1-3 business days.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">📧 Email</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        For anything related to APIRank, email us at:
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        <a href="mailto:contact@apirank.vip" class="text-blue-600 underline font-mono">contact@apirank.vip</a>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Common Inquiries</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">🛠️ Pricing corrections</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We work hard to keep pricing accurate, but AI API prices change frequently.
            If you spot an outdated price, please email us with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mt-2">
            <li>Provider name and model</li>
            <li>Current price on the provider's official pricing page</li>
            <li>URL of the source</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">🤝 Partnership inquiries</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            If you represent an AI API provider and want to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 mt-2">
            <li>Update your provider page (correct specs, add new models)</li>
            <li>Set up an affiliate partnership</li>
            <li>Submit a launch announcement</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2">
            Email us with your provider name and a brief description. We respond within 3 business days.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">📝 Content suggestions</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Have an idea for a comparison, tutorial, or roundup post?
            We prioritize content requests that match what our readers actually search for.
            Send us a topic idea and we'll let you know if we can cover it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">🐛 Bug reports</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Found a broken link, typo, or technical issue? Let us know and we'll fix it fast.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">⚖️ Legal</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            For DMCA notices, takedown requests, or other legal matters, email
            <a href="mailto:contact@apirank.vip" class="text-blue-600 underline">contact@apirank.vip</a>
            with "Legal:" in the subject line.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">💬 Community</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        APIRank doesn't run a Discord or forum (yet), but you can follow updates on:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700">
        <li>Author profile: <a href="https://about.me/jasonxmai" rel="me noopener" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 underline">about.me/jasonxmai</a></li>
        <li>Site RSS feed: <a href="/rss.xml" class="text-blue-600 underline">/rss.xml</a> (when available)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Response Times</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Most inquiries are answered within <strong>1-3 business days</strong>.
        Partnership requests may take up to a week. Bug reports are typically fixed within 24 hours.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          <strong>Note:</strong> APIRank is an independent review site. We are not affiliated with
          OpenAI, Anthropic, DeepSeek, Google, or any of the providers we review. For account-specific
          issues (billing, API keys, support tickets), please contact the provider directly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
